medic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c7553d558294c4eb3ed9fb7c2cc5864517fdf5","tid":45180,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解你自己做廢人要賴落條女度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講多小小<br />\n因為星期一至五都唔會有時間做到自己嘢<br />\n而星期六就要練嘢同返part time<br />\n星期日就陪女朋友<br />\n基本上我嘅生日只係得返讀書，part time，同女朋友<br />\n完全無時間做自己想做嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁又點？都係唔關你女朋友事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e290cb499f46ec58090ae1bca5f5b9d532c59d96","tid":45180,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:57:07.000Z","msg":"幾開心啊，幾好啊，一齊捱一齊努力係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQuit左搵到錢再慢慢玩返音樂打返波囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">冇機會再俾你玩架啦，大個仔啦</span>"},{"pid":"d68f7110bbfc01b7a1be900d239b1190b4bbcef9","tid":45180,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:58:14.000Z","msg":"有無特別原因令你女朋友唔信你？<br />\n你自己揀唔住hall為咗令佢安心定佢叫你唔好住？其實兩者都係你自己揀 唔怪你女朋友事"},{"pid":"efb7c04c6499da130d0313a9992376c20bb46a28","tid":45180,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無特別原因令你女朋友唔信你？<br />\n你自己揀唔住hall為咗令佢安心定佢叫你唔好住？其實兩者都係你自己揀 唔<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關</span></span>你女朋友事</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c61b3802d2cf837fcb9a4179a1e008c2abc3cf8a","tid":45180,"uid":26435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者咁 巴打 如果同條女拍拖可以令你冇左自己咁既 其實究竟你同佢係咪適合繼續呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我諗緊嘅問題<br />\n但係感覺上係錢銀問題<br />\n其實本身屋企環境幾好 奈何我同我老母真係相處唔到，而佢講明出去住就唔會幫我比生活費，所以一定要晒時間做part time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8a29d0c4f4ba32e5e55a83669ac90dba67f0c5","tid":45180,"uid":26435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問巴打咩part time咁高人工  <br />\n夠你係香港呢塊福地自己交租生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n星期一至四私補<br />\n五六做waitor<br />\n經學校搵地方住，所以便宜啲"},{"pid":"65eb243dea25fbc800e1aef9db99790cf2dca9c8","tid":45180,"uid":26435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係要取捨架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者你啱"},{"pid":"2fe18bcd38fdcef2b4f4f5eb554f0601e91ab295","tid":45180,"uid":26435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚憎要踢波但係啲女人嘈生哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾好都冇撚用<br />\nBtw半炒jupas都可以去外國讀medic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好叻，但係份人無乜自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a96ce8d3807c5d7f7587030c47608cd5a7c9316","tid":45180,"uid":26435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾開心啊，幾好啊，一齊捱一齊努力係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQuit左搵到錢再慢慢玩返音樂打返波囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">冇機會再俾你玩架啦，大個仔啦</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你啱 但係我唔甘心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7e790e689a61f597e3204eaad2676f7541b2ea","tid":45180,"uid":21455,"like":0,"dislik